SIM kartlar \u00fc\u00e7 ana boyutta gelir ve telefonlar\u0131n\u0131n herbiri farkl\u0131 boyutta olanlar\u0131 kullanabilir. Bir\u00e7ok operat\u00f6r do\u011fru boyuttaki SIM kart\u0131 sana \u00fccretsiz olarak sa\u011flayacakt\u0131r. \u00d6zel bir SIM kesici aletiyle daha b\u00fcy\u00fck SIM'leri keserek k\u00fc\u00e7\u00fcltebilir veya operat\u00f6r\u00fcnden telefonuna uyumlu bir SIM isteyebilirsin. Daha k\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck SIM'lerin, adapt\u00f6r kart\u0131na yerle\u015ftirilerek daha b\u00fcy\u00fck yuvalara uymas\u0131 sa\u011flanabilir. Operat\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fc de\u011fi\u015ftirdi\u011finde yeni bir SIM karta ihtiyac\u0131n olacak. Yeni bir tarifeye kaydoldu\u011funda bir SIM kart alacaks\u0131n. Operat\u00f6rler aras\u0131 ge\u00e7i\u015f yapar ve sonra farkl\u0131 boyutta bir SIM karta ihtiya\u00e7 duyarsan genellikle m\u00fc\u015fteri hizmetlerine ba\u015fvurarak \u00fccretsiz bir tane alabilirsin. Baz\u0131 operat\u00f6rler (d\u00fcnya genelinde), GSM \u015febekeleri yerine, SIM kart gerektirmeyen CDMA \u015febekelerini kullan\u0131r. Bununla birlikte, \u00e7o\u011fu 4G \u015febekesi GSM \u015febekesidir ve bir SIM kart gerektirir. \u00d6rne\u011fin, Verizon Wireless bir CDMA \u015febekesidir, ancak yine kendi 4G LTE hizmeti bir GSM \u015febekesidir, bu nedenle 4G'ye eri\u015fmek i\u00e7in bir SIM kart gereklidir.

PlayStation\u2019\u0131n ana men\u00fc sisteminde, Ayarlar men\u00fcs\u00fcne ula\u015fana kadar sola kayd\u0131r. Sistem Ayarlar\u0131\u2019n\u0131 bulana kadar a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 kayd\u0131r. A\u015fa\u011f\u0131 kayd\u0131r ve Sistem Bilgisi\u2019ni se\u00e7. MAC adresi, IP adresinin alt\u0131nda listelenecektir. Panodan Sistem Ayarlar\u0131\u2019n\u0131 a\u00e7. A\u011f Ayarlar\u0131n\u0131 a\u00e7 ve A\u011f\u0131 Yap\u0131land\u0131r\u2019\u0131 se\u00e7.  Ek Ayarlar sekmesini se\u00e7 ve sonra Geli\u015fmi\u015f Ayarlar\u2019\u0131 se\u00e7. Alternatif MAC Adresi\u2019ni se\u00e7. MAC adresi ekranda listelenecektir. Tirelerle ayr\u0131lmam\u0131\u015f olabilir. Ana Kanal men\u00fcs\u00fcn\u00fcn sol alt k\u0131sm\u0131ndaki Wii d\u00fc\u011fmesine t\u0131kla. Ayarlar men\u00fcs\u00fcn\u00fcn 2. sayfas\u0131na kayd\u0131r ve \u0130nternet\u2019i se\u00e7. Konsol Bilgisi\u2019ne t\u0131klad\u0131\u011f\u0131nda MAC adresi g\u00f6r\u00fcnt\u00fclenecektir.
K\u00e2\u011f\u0131d\u0131n iki k\u00f6\u015fesi yukar\u0131 ve a\u015fa\u011f\u0131, di\u011feri iki k\u00f6\u015fesi sa\u011fa ve sola bakmal\u0131; t\u0131pk\u0131 bir baklava dilimi gibi.

Bir LAN kurarken, Ethernet \u00fczerinden ka\u00e7 bilgisayar\u0131n a\u011fa ba\u011flanaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 bilmen gerekir. Bu, ihtiyac\u0131n olan port say\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 belirleyecektir. Ba\u011flaman gereken d\u00f6rt veya daha az bilgisayar\u0131n varsa sadece bir y\u00f6nlendiriciye (router) ihtiyac\u0131n olacak. Bilgisayar say\u0131s\u0131 d\u00f6rtten fazla ise y\u00f6nlendiricinde bulunan port say\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 art\u0131rmak i\u00e7in bir a\u011f anahtar\u0131 (switch) alman gerekir. Ayg\u0131tlar\u0131n kablosuz olarak ba\u011flanmas\u0131na izin vermek istiyorsan, kablosuz bir a\u011f yay\u0131nlayabilen bir y\u00f6nlendiriciye ihtiyac\u0131n olacakt\u0131r. Bir ma\u011fazadan ya da \u0130nternet'ten alaca\u011f\u0131n y\u00f6nlendiricilerin \u00e7o\u011fu kablosuz \u00f6zelli\u011fe sahiptir. A\u011f anahtarlar\u0131 kablosuz ba\u011flant\u0131 sa\u011flamaz ve sadece kablolu LAN'lar i\u00e7in veya y\u00f6nlendiricideki port say\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 art\u0131rmak i\u00e7in kullan\u0131labilir. Ba\u011fl\u0131 t\u00fcm cihazlar\u0131n \u0130nternet'e eri\u015fmesini istiyorsan ba\u011flant\u0131lar\u0131 y\u00f6netmek i\u00e7in bir y\u00f6nlendiriciye ihtiyac\u0131n olacak. E\u011fer cihazlar\u0131n \u0130nternet'e ba\u011flanmas\u0131na ihtiyac\u0131n yoksa sadece bir a\u011f anahtar\u0131 kullanabilirsin. Bu, \u00e7o\u011fu evde sorun de\u011fildir, ancak a\u011f kablolar\u0131 100 metreden daha uzun de\u011fildir.

\u0130nternet eri\u015fimini ge\u00e7ici olarak devre d\u0131\u015f\u0131 b\u0131rakmak istiyorsan ancak bunu her yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131nda g\u00fcvenlik duvar\u0131 ayarlar\u0131nda gezinmek istemiyorsan bu programlar kullan\u0131\u015fl\u0131 olabilir. Belki baz\u0131 i\u015fleri \u00e7evrimd\u0131\u015f\u0131 yapmak istiyor ancak kendini \u0130nternet'i kullanma olas\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan tamamen soyutlamak istemiyorsundur. Genellikle t\u00fcm siteleri veya yaln\u0131zca belirli siteleri devre d\u0131\u015f\u0131 b\u0131rakmay\u0131 se\u00e7ebilirsin. Bu uygulama, bilgisayar\u0131n\u0131n \u0130nternet eri\u015fimini ge\u00e7ici olarak devre d\u0131\u015f\u0131 b\u0131rakarak \u0130nternet'ten \u201czorla\u201d uzakla\u015fmana yard\u0131mc\u0131 olacakt\u0131r. Bu k\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck komut dosyas\u0131, Windows bilgisayar\u0131nda bir t\u0131klamayla \u0130nternet'i tamamen devre d\u0131\u015f\u0131 b\u0131rakman\u0131 sa\u011flar. \u0130nternet ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 daha sonra istedi\u011fin zaman yine bir t\u0131klamayla geri getirebilirsin. Ba\u015flamak i\u00e7in, Toggle-Internet.bat dosyas\u0131n\u0131 masa\u00fcst\u00fcne indir. Toggle masa\u00fcst\u00fc simgesine sa\u011f t\u0131kla. \u201cY\u00f6netici Olarak \u00c7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u201d\u0131 se\u00e7ti\u011fin anda \u0130nternet ba\u011flant\u0131n kesilecek. Daha sonra, yeniden ba\u011flanman gerekti\u011finde, ayn\u0131 dosyaya sa\u011f t\u0131kla ve \u00f6nceki gibi y\u00f6netici olarak \u00e7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. D\u00e2

Bunu VMware \u00fczerinden yap. Bunu \"Hardware\" (Donan\u0131m) adl\u0131 s\u00fctunun alt\u0131nda bulursun. \"Disk Provisioning\"in (Disk Sa\u011flama) alt\u0131ndaki pencerenin sa\u011f taraf\u0131nda diskinin \"Provisioned Size\"\u0131n\u0131 (Sa\u011flanan Boyut) belirle. Baz\u0131 d\u00fczenlerde \"Utilities\" (\u0130zlenceler) ad\u0131nda a\u00e7\u0131l\u0131r bir men\u00fc bulunur. Burada \"Expand\"i (Geni\u015flet) se\u00e7. Genelde disk boyutu bu a\u015famada 30 ila 40 GB olur. Boyutu ilk ba\u015fta 45 ila 55 GB aras\u0131na getirmeyi dene. Bu, sanal diskin yeni azami boyutunu ayarlar. Diskinin boyutunu geni\u015fletmi\u015f olsan da i\u015fletim sistemi \u00fczerinden yapman gereken birka\u00e7 \u015fey daha vard\u0131r. Diskini yeniden taramak i\u00e7in Disk Y\u00f6netimi'ne git ve Diskleri Yeniden Tara'y\u0131 se\u00e7. Y\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fc sabah ve ak\u015fam birer kez ve y\u00fcz\u00fcn her terledi\u011finde y\u0131ka.  \u00d6rne\u011fin, y\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fc egzersiz \u00f6ncesi ve sonras\u0131 ve fiziksel \u00e7aba gerektiren bir i\u015f yapt\u0131ktan sonra y\u0131kamak iyi bir fikirdir. Spor \u00e7antanda ya da c\u00fczdan\u0131nda makyaj\u0131n\u0131 silebilece\u011fin ve cildini temizleyebilece\u011fin birka\u00e7 makyaj temizleme mendili bulundurmay\u0131 dene. \u0130\u015fe, y\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fc \u0131l\u0131k suyla \u0131slatarak ba\u015fla. Sadece lavaboya e\u011filip y\u00fcz\u00fcne biraz \u0131l\u0131k su \u00e7arpabilirsin. En iyisi, y\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fc hafif bir y\u00fcz temizleyicisiyle temizlemektir. Az miktarda temizleyiciyi ellerine d\u00f6k ve ellerinle ve parmak u\u00e7lar\u0131nla cildine masaj yaparak s\u00fcr. Cildini tahri\u015f edebilece\u011fi i\u00e7in, ovu\u015fturmaktan ka\u00e7\u0131n. Y\u00fcz temizleyicini s\u00fcrmen bitince

Dudaklar\u0131n\u0131n nemli kalmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flamak sa\u011fl\u0131kl\u0131, pembe \u0131\u015f\u0131lt\u0131y\u0131 korumas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flayacakt\u0131r. Bu \u00f6zellikle dudaklar\u0131 a\u015f\u0131r\u0131 derecede kurutabilen \u00e7ok s\u0131cak ya da \u00e7ok so\u011fuk havalarda \u00f6nemlidir.  Her gece yatmadan \u00f6nce nemlendirici bir dudak balm\u0131 s\u00fcr ve g\u00fcn i\u00e7inde nemlendirici rujlar\u0131 tercih et. Balmumu bazl\u0131 \u00fcr\u00fcnler son derece nemlendirici olabilir. K\u0131\u015f\u0131n nemi dudaklar\u0131na hapsetmek ve dudaklar\u0131n\u0131n kurumas\u0131n\u0131 \u00f6nlemek i\u00e7in petrol j\u00f6lesini dene. Daha do\u011fal nemlendirme y\u00f6ntemlerini tercih ediyorsan dudaklar\u0131na biraz bal (ama yalama) ya da biraz aloe vera s\u00fcrmeyi dene. Dudaklar\u0131n\u0131 bol bol su i\u00e7erek de nemlendirebilirsin; ideal olarak g\u00fcnde alt\u0131 ila sekiz bardak su i\u00e7melisin. Peeling cildin rengi bozulmu\u015f \u00fcst katmanlar\u0131n\u0131 soyup alttaki a\u00e7\u0131k pembe rengi ortaya \u00e7\u0131kard\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u00e7in koyu renkli dudaklar\u0131n rengini a\u00e7man\u0131n harika bir yoludur.  Bir tatl\u0131 ka\u015f\u0131\u011f\u0131 zeytinya\u011f\u0131yla bir tatl\u0131 ka\u015f\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u015fekeri kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131rarak kendi dudak peeling\u2019ini yap. Bu kar\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131 parmaklar\u0131nla dudaklar\u0131na s\u00fcr\u00fcp hafif\u00e7e ovala. G\u00fczel ve yumu\u015fak dudaklara kavu\u015fmak i\u00e7in su

Dudaklar\u0131n\u0131 bol bol su i\u00e7erek de nemlendirebilirsin; ideal olarak g\u00fcnde alt\u0131 ila sekiz bardak su i\u00e7melisin. Peeling cildin rengi bozulmu\u015f \u00fcst katmanlar\u0131n\u0131 soyup alttaki a\u00e7\u0131k pembe rengi ortaya \u00e7\u0131kard\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u00e7in koyu renkli dudaklar\u0131n rengini a\u00e7man\u0131n harika bir yoludur.  Bir tatl\u0131 ka\u015f\u0131\u011f\u0131 zeytinya\u011f\u0131yla bir tatl\u0131 ka\u015f\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u015fekeri kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131rarak kendi dudak peeling\u2019ini yap. Bu kar\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131 parmaklar\u0131nla dudaklar\u0131na s\u00fcr\u00fcp hafif\u00e7e ovala. G\u00fczel ve yumu\u015fak dudaklara kavu\u015fmak i\u00e7in su

C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00e1c nhau trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean vi\u1ebft c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng gi\u1eefa ph\u1ea7n m\u1edf b\u00e0i, m\u1ed7i \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u0103n trong th\u00e2n b\u00e0i, v\u00e0 k\u1ebft b\u00e0i. Khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft m\u1ea1ch l\u1ea1c.  B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang ph\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft \u0111o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft b\u00e0i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ebft, \"\u0110\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn....\", b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c. V\u00ed d\u1ee5, h\u00e3y th\u1eed d\u00f9ng, \"Sau c\u00f9ng,...\" ho\u1eb7c \"Nh\u01b0 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng minh...\". \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb nh\u01b0, \"\u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh\", \"K\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp\", ho\u1eb7c \"M\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn kh\u00e1c\" \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1. B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0o \u0111o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft b\u00e0i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 b\u00e0i lu\u1eadn. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tan bi\u1ebfn do ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda c\u1ea9u th\u1ea3. H\u00e3y d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi n\u1ed9p b\u00e0i.  T\u00ecm c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i ch\u00ednh t\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p. H\u00e3y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m tra ch\u00ednh t\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3

B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean bu\u1ed9c iPad kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u00e1y ho\u1eb7c n\u1ebfu n\u00fat \"Sleep/Wake\" kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i. Thao t\u00e1c bu\u1ed9c iPad kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a l\u01b0u c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t. N\u00fat \"Sleep/Wake\" h\u00ecnh b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c n\u00e0y \u1edf g\u00f3c tr\u00ean b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i khung iPad khi \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ee9ng theo chi\u1ec1u d\u1ecdc. Ph\u00edm \"Home\" h\u00ecnh tr\u00f2n n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a iPad.  \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y iPad \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i. Sau khi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh kh\u00f3a (Lock Screen) tr\u00ean iPad hi\u1ec7n ra, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. Sau khi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i, iPad s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9ng n\u1eefa; v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n m\u00e1y b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00fat \"Sleep/Wake\":  Nh\u1ea5n gi\u1eef n\u00fat \"Sleep/Wake\" cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi c\u00f4ng t\u1eafc \"slide to power off\" hi\u1ec7n ra. Vu\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng t\u1eafc \"slide to power off\" sang ph\u1ea3i. Ch\u1edd m\u00e0n hinh iPad chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u00e0u \u0111en.

B\u00f3n ph\u00e2n cho c\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00fac cho hoa n\u1edf r\u1ed9. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3n ph\u00e2n qu\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0m c\u00e2y t\u0103ng t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, v\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y c\u00e2y tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1eadm r\u1ea1p, h\u00e3y c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m ph\u00e2n b\u00f3n.  Ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m v\u01b0\u1eddn tr\u1ed3ng hoa gi\u1ea5y b\u00f3n ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 1:1:1 ho\u1eb7c 2:1:2, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n b\u00f3n v\u1edbi n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ed1t ph\u00e1t cao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay l\u00fac tr\u1ed3ng. Ph\u00e2n b\u00f3n h\u1eefu c\u01a1 ho\u1eb7c ph\u00e2n b\u00f3n ch\u1eadm tan ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.  H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u00f3n ph\u00e2n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n trong n\u0103m v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u00e2y hoa gi\u1ea5y c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 che ph\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u00edch c\u00e2y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec5n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ee9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 treo nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng d\u00e2y kim lo\u1ea1i song song d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u00e2y che ph\u1ee7. B\u1ebb cong nh\u1eefng c\u00e0nh hoa gi\u1ea5y v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00f3 v\u00e0o ph\u00eda sau c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng d\u00e2y kim lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y. Quan s\u00e1t s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi hoa gi\u1ea5y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u lan tr\u00ean t

SOS Online Backup - M\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c trong vi\u1ec7c sao l\u01b0u game, SOS cung c\u1ea5p kho l\u01b0u tr\u1eef kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n. D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Google Drive, SkyDrive (OneDrive) v\u00e0 DropBox cung c\u1ea5p l\u01b0u tr\u1eef tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng. T\u1eadp tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb d\u00f9ng t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu t\u1eadp tin b\u1ecb x\u00f3a tr\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ee7 sao l\u01b0u th\u00ec n\u00f3 b\u1ecb x\u00f3a tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i! Write down each event in your script on their own note cards. This way you can easily reorganize the events to see what works best. Write down all of your ideas, even if you think they're bad, since you may not know what will work best in your final script. If you don't want to use index cards, you may also use a word document or screenwriting software, such as WriterDuet or Final Draft. Once you write all of your ideas on cards, lay them out on a table or floor and organize them in the chronological order of your story. Look at how certain events lead into one another to see if it makes sense.

Existen muchos servicios para esto, tanto gratuitos como de pago, que ofrecen un rango de caracter\u00edsticas muy amplio:   BackBlaze: ofrece almacenamiento ilimitado y cuenta con una tarifa mensual muy baja. Carbonite: uno de los servicios de copias de seguridad en l\u00ednea m\u00e1s consolidado. Carbonite ofrece almacenamiento ilimitado a cambio de una tarifa mensual. SOS Online Backup: otro de los jugadores viejos en el \u00e1rea, SOS ofrece almacenamiento ilimitado para todos los tipos de cuentas.

Si detectas zarig\u00fceyas en las c\u00e1maras (por ejemplo, el techo o debajo de la casa), es probable que tengas que eliminarlas f\u00edsicamente. Puedes conseguir una trampa de jaula para capturarlas con vida en una tienda de mejoras para el hogar o un minorista a trav\u00e9s de internet. Estas jaulas sirven para capturar animales con vida sin da\u00f1arlos ni matarlos. Adem\u00e1s, son preferibles a las trampas de muerte instant\u00e1nea.  Ten en cuenta que, en muchos estados y municipios, puede estar restringido o prohibido el uso de trampas de muerte instant\u00e1nea para deshacerte de las zarig\u00fceyas. Sin embargo, el uso de trampas de jaula que mantienen con vida a la presa rara vez est\u00e1 prohibido. Averigua en tu municipio si existen restricciones para las capturas. Es probable que algunas ciudades requieran un permiso. Otras pueden presentar demandas espec\u00edficas acerca de d\u00f3nde liberar al animal y qui\u00e9n puede hacerlo.

Puedes mejorar la gesti\u00f3n analizando la informaci\u00f3n que contiene. En concreto, puedes tratar de comprender cu\u00e1ntos productos necesitas en un momento determinado y cu\u00e1ndo tendr\u00e1s que ordenar m\u00e1s. Primero, calcula el costo diario de los productos vendidos, dividiendo el costo anual o trimestral de los productos vendidos entre el n\u00famero de d\u00edas que abri\u00f3 tu negocio durante ese tiempo. Despu\u00e9s, divide el valor actual de tu inventario entre esta cantidad. El resultado representar\u00e1 el per\u00edodo de inversi\u00f3n promedio de tu inventario.  Esta cifra representa el tiempo promedio que tardan los productos que compraste convertirse en ventas. Luego, puedes trabajar para reducir esta cifra, ordenando una menor cantidad de productos o procurando recibir pagos m\u00e1s r\u00e1pidos de tus clientes. Tambi\u00e9n puedes hallar la proporci\u00f3n entre el inventario y las ventas dividiendo el valor de tu inventario entre las ventas mensuales. Monitorea este valor para saber si aumenta o disminuye.
